Code for computing various P_BLAH quantities in a general way from PE
samples.
about.summary: Code for computing various P_BLAH quantities in a general way from PE samples.

name: pepredicates
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pepredicates" %}
{% set version = "0.0.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: de2addf01e2bccbf361f729c21693f3dc56690caec9abfa75c5a118f1e9f4cfd

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools
  run:
    - astropy
    - matplotlib-base
    - numpy
    - python >=3.6
    - seaborn

test:
  imports:
    - pepredicates

about:
  home: https://charlie.hoy.docs.ligo.org/pepredicates/index.html
  doc_url: https://charlie.hoy.docs.ligo.org/pepredicates/index.html
  license: AGPL-3.0
  license_family: AGPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Code for computing various P_BLAH quantities in a general way from PE samples.
  description: |
    Code for computing various P_BLAH quantities in a general way from PE
    samples.
extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hoyc1
